  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 31:21",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Deuteronomy 31:21",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "This song shall testify against them as a witness — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That they were sufficiently admonished of their duty, and forewarned what would be the consequence of their defection from me and my worship, (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 32:18-19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",) and be a clear evidence that the calamities which befall them are judgments sent from me for the punishment of their transgressions. How ought this to be remarked with wonder! For, to this very day, above three thousand years after, this song is a strong proof and demonstration, both to Jews and Christians, that Moses did indeed speak by the commandment of God. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "I know their imagination — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Inclination to idolatry, which they do not check as they ought: and some of them do not only cherish it in their hearts, but, as far as they can and dare, secretly practise it, as may be gathered from ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Amos 5:25",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 7:43",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
